FBIS3-51463 "drlat011_a_94011" FBIS-LAT-94-011 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Jan 1994 CARIBBEAN Chief of Cuban Navy Visits St. Petersburg FL1501013494 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 0000 GMT 15 Jan 94 FL1501013494 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] ITAR-TASS has reported that on 14 January Rear Admiral Pedro Perez Betancourt, chief of the Cuban Revolutionary Navy, visited military sites in St. Petersburg during his third day of his visit to Russia. Perez Betancourt is visiting Russia as a guest of Admiral Feliks Gromov, commander of the Russian Fleet. He visited the Kustnezov Naval Academy and the main headquarters of Navigation and Oceanography in the former Leningrad.
